WEBVTT

00:00.077 --> 00:06.209
My father loves coffee, drinks coffee every day, but makes coffee so wrong.

00:06.603 --> 00:10.135
I think he puts like, maybe two tablespoons in the whole pot so it just tastes like water.

00:10.417 --> 00:11.577
And I keep trying to tell him,...

00:11.683 --> 00:14.514
..."Dad, you have to put more coffee in here," but it doesn't work.

00:14.773 --> 00:17.021
So with Blonde, I think he gets the flavor that he likes,...

00:17.136 --> 00:20.055
...and so he feels more comfortable putting the appropriate amount of coffee in the thing.

00:20.525 --> 00:20.889
He does.

00:21.039 --> 00:21.791
Jerry likes it light.

